To analyze further the 5′ region of the MT5-MMP gene sequence, primers were designed to amplify the divergent region ( Table 1 C). Expected bands at 978 and 1140
bp represented MT5-MMPvar and MT5-MMP transcripts, respectively. Results from RT-PCR analysis demonstrated the presence of both transcripts in NT2 cells, hNT cells, and in adult human brain samples ( Fig. 3
).
